pos_examples: Now, saw board teddy into medium part frame_9 using saw yew with awood rain, surface object_50, changing size from aboardsize object_260 to aboardsize object_260_62 through aboardsize object_260_62_34.
(do-saw-medium teddy frame_9 yew rain object_50 object_260 object_260_62_34 object_260_62)

Once you are done, please cut board teddy into part frame_9 using highspeed-saw kumquat_8 with awood rain, surface dress_red, changing size from aboardsize object_260 to aboardsize object_260_62_34 via intermediate sizes aboardsize object_260_62_34_45 and aboardsize object_260_85.
(cut-board-large teddy frame_9 kumquat_8 rain dress_red object_260 object_260_85 object_260_62_34_45 object_260_62_34)

First, do immersion varnish on part frame_9 using immersion-varnisher fire to change color to acolour roof_11 with surface dress_red and then saw board teddy into small part frame_9 using saw yew with awood rain, surface object_50, changing size from aboardsize object_260 to aboardsize object_260_62_34.

(do-immersion-varnish frame_9 fire roof_11 dress_red)
(do-saw-small teddy frame_9 yew rain object_50 object_260 object_260_62_34)
The next step is to unload board teddy from highspeed-saw kumquat_8.
